{"tid":2510014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聾人家庭與聾貓｜貓咪識睇手語解救受困主人　收養聾貓學懂聾不是缺陷","createTime":"2021-04-30T00:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T00:51:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c7953992ce05a4da0d1ef5e18cbb1788be7777","tid":2510014,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:43:18.000Z","msg":"拍攝前，Anita已經提醒我，她們的貓有點怕人，果然甫進門，五隻貓早已躲得不知所蹤，只剩下剛睡醒的聾貓芝麻，躺在門邊一臉無措地看着我和攝影師。Anita用手語解釋，「因為平時我們不會說話，家裏沒有聲音，突然有健聽的人來到，有人說話、發出聲音，貓咪就會很驚慌，全部躲起來。」只有芝麻因為聽不到，在其他貓咪聞聲而逃時仍然呼呼大睡，懵然不知有人類入侵。<br />\n<br />\nAnita一家四口都是聾人，她先天失聰，妹妹Brenda則因年幼時發燒而致，Brenda形容她們的聽覺，戴上助聽器後會聽到少許聲音，例如聽到有人在附近談話，但具體內容就聽不清楚。雖然她們聽不到貓叫聲、貓「煲水」的呼嚕聲，但無阻她們領養六隻貓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210430/QGLJNVKWY5BS5OXLJIO5WU35N4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210430%2FQGLJNVKWY5BS5OXLJIO5WU35N4%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=953ce2ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210430%2FQGLJNVKWY5BS5OXLJIO5WU35N4%2F&h=1b455893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210430/QGLJNVKWY5BS5OXLJIO5WU35N4/</a>"},{"pid":"5eedd42d6b52d191122e4a17d8273ec765811cb0","tid":2510014,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:45:21.000Z","msg":"好打耳!! 請名跟進"},{"pid":"91dd2c55f9c20b92fc45599f8cc3855576a9f677","tid":2510014,"uid":93599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:51:32.000Z","msg":"聽唔到煲水聲都feel到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地少左一樣養貓既麻煩野<br />\n有時俾貓叫醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}